DATA ATTRIBUTION (the MIT terms above cover the source code only)

The air-raid alert dataset analysed by this software is not covered by this
license. It is collected and published by Vadym Klymenko ("Vadimkin") in the
repository "ukrainian-air-raid-sirens-dataset"
(https://github.com/Vadimkin/ukrainian-air-raid-sirens-dataset). The underlying
alert messages originate from the official "@air_alert_ua" Telegram channel of
Ukraine's state air-raid alert system. If you reuse the data, please credit
both the collector and the original alert channel, and consult the source
repository for its own terms.
